            "text_color": "#1C2E23"
          }
        },
        "agitate_text_3": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Here's what the TRT industry won't tell you: published research shows that gut microbiome composition directly modulates testosterone production through the gut-brain-gonad axis. When key bacterial populations deplete — a pattern documented in every immigrant diaspora community studied — the upstream system that drives testosterone breaks down. You don't have a hormone problem. You have a microbiome problem.</p><p><strong>TRT: $150–400/month plus blood work, plus lifetime dependency. Origin: $34/month. No needles. No shutdown.</strong></p>",
            "text_color": "#1C2E23"
          }
